      "source": [
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "\n",
        "# Monod fonksiyonu (kinetik denklem)\n",
        "def monod(S, mu_max, K_S):\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    Î¼(S) = Î¼max * S / (K_S + S)\n",
        "    S: substrat (g/L)\n",
        "    mu_max: maksimum bÃ¼yÃ¼me hÄ±zÄ± (1/h)\n",
        "    K_S: yarÄ± doygunluk sabiti (g/L)\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    return mu_max * S / (K_S + S)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Dashboard iÃ§in sÃ¼rekli S ekseni (0.1-100 g/L aralÄ±ÄÄ±nda 200 nokta)\n",
        "S_range = np.linspace(0.1, 100, 200)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "H13iy6J_QwQA"
      },
      "execution_count": 7,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "from ipywidgets import interact, FloatSlider, Checkbox\n",
        "\n",
        "def monod_plot(mu_max=1.0, K_S=20.0, show_data=True):\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    mu_max ve K_S slider'larÄ±yla Monod eÄrisini canlÄ± gÃ¼nceller.\n",
        "    show_data=True ise deneysel (S_mid, Î¼_est) noktalarÄ±nÄ± da Ã§izer.\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    Î¼ = monod(S_range, mu_max, K_S)\n",
        "\n",
        "    plt.figure(figsize=(7,5))\n",
        "    plt.plot(S_range, Î¼, linewidth=2, label=f\"Monod fit (Î¼max={mu_max:.2f}, K_S={K_S:.1f})\")\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Ä°stenirse deneysel noktalarÄ± da gÃ¶ster (HÃ¼cre 2'de oluÅturulan monod_df'den)\n",
        "    if show_data and 'monod_df' in globals():\n",
        "        plt.scatter(monod_df[\"S_mid\"], monod_df[\"mu_est\"], s=55, alpha=0.85, label=\"Data (S_mid vs Î¼)\")\n",
        "    elif show_data:\n",
        "        print(\"UyarÄ±: monod_df bulunamadÄ±. (HÃ¼cre 2'yi Ã§alÄ±ÅtÄ±rdÄ±ÄÄ±ndan emin ol.)\")\n",
        "\n",
        "    plt.xlabel(\"Substrate (S, g/L)\")\n",
        "    plt.ylabel(\"Growth rate Î¼ (1/h)\")\n",
        "    plt.title(\"Interactive Monod Dashboard\")\n",
        "    plt.grid(True)\n",
        "    plt.legend()\n",
        "    plt.show()\n",
        "\n",
